Actions.Text: HELD FOR CONSIDERATION IN REAL PROPERTY TAXATION

Title: Authorizes the West Babylon Church of God of Prophecy, Inc., to file an application for retroactive real property tax exemption
Summary: Authorizes the West Babylon Church of God of Prophecy, Inc. to file an application for retroactive real property tax exemption with the assessor of the town of Babylon, county of Suffolk, with respect to the 2018-2019 assessment rolls.
ActClause: AN ACT authorizing the West Babylon Church of God of Prophecy Inc., to file an application for retroactive real property tax exemption
